CREATE TABLE viewer_demographics ( viewer_id INT PRIMARY KEY, age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), location VARCHAR(50) );
CREATE TABLE viewer_preferences ( viewer_id INT PRIMARY KEY, genre VARCHAR(50), language VARCHAR(20), rating DECIMAL(3,2) );
CREATE TABLE viewers_interaction ( interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY, viewer_id INT, interaction_type VARCHAR(20), timestamp TIMESTAMP );
CREATE TABLE viewer_activity ( activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY, viewer_id INT, action_taken VARCHAR(50), timestamp TIMESTAMP );
CREATE TABLE viewer_feedback ( feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY, viewer_id INT, feedback_text TEXT, rating DECIMAL(3,2), timestamp TIMESTAMP );
